tweet: Govt's offer of suspending farm laws for 18 months would have to be done by a law passed in Parliament or an ordinance. It cannot be done by a govt notification. If the govt is willing to pass a law to suspend, why not just withdraw the laws&bring a new law after full discussion?
name: Prashant Bhushan

tweet: Today (21 Jan), VCK is set to hold demonstrations in all district headquarters demanding Modi Govt to repeal the three farm laws, and demanding the TN Govt to issue an ordinance on Minimum Support Price (MSP).   In Chennai, protest near Valluvar Kottam at 10am.  https://t.co/C75zWy7ll1
name: Thol. Thirumavalavan
